        What to Expect When Selling in Newstead
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Newstead is Brisbane's most transformed inner suburb. Selling here is mostly an apartment story, and it requires a specific approach to extract full value.
      </p>
